wikipedia_page.main: Alfred James Wheeler (4 April 1910 – 1978) was an English professional footballer who played as a forward for various clubs in the Football League in the 1930s.

response: * Alf Wheeler (footballer, born 1910) (1910–1978), English footballer who played for Walsall, Northampton Town, Southampton and Gillingham
* Alf Wheeler (footballer, born 1922) (1922–2013), English footballer who played for Blackburn Rovers and Swindon Town
* Alf Wheeler (Australian footballer) (1885–1929), Australian rules footballer
